Product backlog is the pending list of items to be developed. product owner manages the product backlog, which is owned by the product owner.
the items are generally represented in form of user stories, the product backlog can undergo changes anytime during 
the project and groomed across the sprint
 
the INVEST principle coined by bill wake can be used for writing good user stories and reviewing them.

I - Independent
N - Negotiate
V - Valuable
E - Estimate
S - Small
T - Testable
